Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}你拿着锁。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我拿着钥匙。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}一直贴身保管着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}等哪一天我们都长大 再会的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}用这钥匙将锁里的东西取出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}然后就
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚吧
